2018年，房協花費2,000萬翻新漁光村而成的「暫住租屋」過渡性房屋出租計劃提供1至3人單位3個類別，面積從1人單位的14平方米至最大3人單位的28平方米，暫租費用介乎560至1400元<ref name=hkhs_180712>{{cite news |title=房協推出「暫租住屋」過渡性房屋計劃 |url=https://www.hkhs.com/home/upload/pdf/pr_20180706_Transitional%20Rental%20Housing%20Scheme_YKC%20(TC)_20180712113832.pdf |date=2018-07-12 |accessdate=2018-10-22 |work=香港房屋協會 |archive-date=2018-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181022232716/https://www.hkhs.com/home/upload/pdf/pr_20180706_Transitional%20Rental%20Housing%20Scheme_YKC%20(TC)_20180712113832.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=東網181022>{{cite news |title=漁光村過渡屋最快下周四入伙 暫20%翻新妥 |url=http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181022/bkn-20181022153242755-1022_00822_001.html |date=2018-10-22 |agency=東網 |accessdate=2018-10-22 |archive-date=2018-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181023034822/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181022/bkn-20181022153242755-1022_00822_001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

